video.title: Cupcake Wars Collection
video.synopsis: The best cupcake bakers in the country battle to see who makes the best cupcakes. In this war of frosting and sugar, there is only one winner.

episodes.synopsis: Four out-of-this-world cupcake bakers will fight for the chance to have their tasty treats at a VIP party honoring the first man in space.
episodes.title: Cupcakes: The Final Frontier

episodes.synopsis: Four artful cupcake bakers will compete for the chance to have their cupcakes featured at a party celebrating the art of director Tim Burton.
episodes.title: Tim Burton Bake-Off

episodes.synopsis: Four talented cupcake makers go head-to-head in hopes of having their cupcake creations at the center of an exclusive party for the Festival of Arts.
episodes.title: Work of Art

episodes.synopsis: Four talented bakers will have to use their superpowers if they want a chance to serve their cupcakes at Comic-Con's exclusive Masquerade Party.
episodes.title: Comic Con Cupcakes

episodes.synopsis: Four talented bakers vie for the chance to have their cupcake creations take center stage at country star Jennette McCurdy's record release party.
episodes.title: Jennette McCurdy Cupcakes

episodes.synopsis: Four bakers compete for their cupcakes to take center stage at a VIP party for the opera world's biggest stars.
episodes.title: Cupcake Love Story

episodes.synopsis: It's monster truck madness as four bakers battle for a place at the VIP Pre-Race Pit Party for Monster Truck Jam.
episodes.title: Monster Cupcakes

episodes.synopsis: Four vegan bakers fight to have their cupcakes at the opening day celebration for the inaugural Los Angeles Green Festival.
episodes.title: Vegan Bake-Off

episodes.synopsis: It's time to laugh out loud as four cupcake bakers try to take their cupcakes viral at a VIP party for FunnyOrDie.com.
episodes.title: Funny or Die

episodes.synopsis: The men of "Cupcake Wars" go to battle as four returning bakers compete for a place at the VIP party for the hit show "Yo Gabba Gabba Live."
episodes.title: Yo Gabba Gabba

episodes.synopsis: It's a race to the finish line as four cupcake bakers fight for a place at a VIP party celebrating the 2012 Los Angeles Marathon.
episodes.title: L.A. Marathon

episodes.synopsis: Four returning "Cupcake Wars" champions compete to serve their cupcakes at a black tie gala celebrating the 70th anniversary of the USO.
episodes.title: Saluting the USO

episodes.synopsis: TV star Kristin Cavallari will be expecting great cupcakes as four talented bakers compete to serve their sweet treats at her baby shower.
episodes.title: Kristin Cavallari Baby Shower

episodes.synopsis: It will be happily ever after for one cupcake maker who wins the opportunity to serve cupcakes at a spectacular Match.com wedding event.
episodes.title: A Perfect Match.com

episodes.synopsis: The fur will be flying as four bakers fight for the opportunity to serve their cupcakes at a members-only party at the world-famous San Diego Zoo.
episodes.title: San Diego Zoo

episodes.synopsis: Four all-star bakers handpicked by fans will compete for the chance to serve their cupcakes at a celebrity-packed charity gala hosted by Lance Bass.
episodes.title: Fan Favorites

episodes.synopsis: Four bakers compete to launch their cupcakes into the stratosphere at a gala celebrating the arrival of the space shuttle Endeavour in Los Angeles.
episodes.title: Cosmic Cupcakes

episodes.synopsis: Four bakers have to bring the funny -- and the tasty -- if they want to be front and center at a celebrity-packed VIP party for "Variety" magazine.
episodes.title: Comedy Cupcakes

episodes.synopsis: Four talented cupcake bakers fight for the chance to win $10,000 and serve their cupcakes at a party for Jessica Alba's new brand, the Honest Company.
episodes.title: The Honest Company

episodes.synopsis: Bad-girl bakers battle to win the hearts of special guest judges WWE Divas Alicia Fox and Layla and bring their cupcakes to WWE's SummerSlam.
episodes.title: WWE SummerSlam

episodes.synopsis: Four teams of mother-daughter bakers fight to have their delicious cupcakes at the center of a Los Angeles bridal bash and win $10,000.
episodes.title: L.A. Bridal Bash

episodes.synopsis: Four bakers fight to win the right to serve vegan cupcakes at Rob Zombie's latest venture: the Great American Nightmare, a haunted music attraction.
episodes.title: Great American Nightmare

episodes.synopsis: Four bakers vying for a chance to serve sweet treats at the Aquarium of the Pacific must create a delicious cupcake out of sustainable seafood.
episodes.title: Aquarium of the Pacific

episodes.synopsis: Love is in the air as four bakers vie to bring their cupcakes to Match.com's Stir Events by uniting men's favorite foods with women's favorites.
episodes.title: Match.com

episodes.synopsis: It's the mother of all horse races as four bakers vie for the chance to have their cupcakes at the legendary Breeders' Cup World Championships.
episodes.title: Breeders' Cup
